reviewText: Neat to see how these dolls are made.
Very interesting ... but a bit too short !
The DVD was interesting and informative. I would recommend this DVD to anyone who has an interest in nesting dolls (matryoshka)

I enjoyed watching the dvd, but the two people narrating it were a little stiff and I think might have tried to be more at ease.  The subject was interesting, and I loved watching the dolls being made.
